T1  - Is board compensation excessive?
AU  - Dah, Mustafa A.
AU  - Frye, Melissa B.
JO  - Journal of Corporate Finance
VL  - 45
SP  - 566
EP  - 585
PY  - 2017
DA  - 2017/08/01/
